s, not UserStore — they are not interchangeable.\",\"scope\":\"auth\"},{\"kind\":\"convention\",\"text\":\"Route handlers in this project live at src/app/(frontend)/api/ not src/app/api/ — the (frontend) segment matters for routing.\",\"scope\":\"src/app\"},{\"kind\":\"convention\",\"text\":\"API handlers follow a standard middleware chain: withAuth HOC → rate-limiter → handler, all returning Result<T, E>.\",\"scope\":\"API handlers\"},{\"kind\":\"convention\",\"text\":\"Input validation uses Zod schemas imported from src/validation/ at the API boundary before any service calls.\",\"scope\":\"src/validation\"}]}","createdAt":"2026-04-18T17:10:47.655Z","wordCount":715,"positions":[2,10,18,31,38,47,54,67,75,81,96,104,109,123,129,140,144,165,169,188,196,205,212,225,232,238,255,263,271,275,280,290,295,299,303,307,319,329,337,349,360,368,372,380,387,400,407,411,420,429,438,449,456,465,471,476,486,499,509,525,533,537,550,557,570,577,583,594,599,603,611,625,629,648,652,661,668,672,680,689,697,701]}},"totalDocs":2}